product.name: York Wallcoverings NZ0786 Grasscloth Wallpaper by River Grass, Black, Cream, Beige, Khaki, Tan
product.description: Midnight at the oasis. And this is the sophisticated look for just such an exotic locale. Or for an Asian setting, and how striking in a contemporary American home! the juxtaposition of neutral shades of beige and cream with the ebony background elevates this grass cloth to the next level of nouveau classic organic home decor.
